longBusinessSummary: Foxby Corp. is a closed ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by CEF Advisers, Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It was formerly known as LCM Internet Growth Fund, Inc. Foxby Corp. was formed on August 24, 1998 and is domiciled in the United States.
